   1:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner.cpp **** /**
   2:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner.cpp ****  * mpr121_glass_tuner.cpp ‚Äî MPR121 Sensitivity Tuner for Glass-Covered Electrodes
   3:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner.cpp ****  * Daisy Seed ‚Äî Bit-Bang I2C  (SDA=D12, SCL=D11)
   4:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner.cpp ****  *
   5:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner.cpp ****  * Sweeps CDC (charge current) and CDT (charge time) combinations,
   6:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner.cpp ****  * measures SNR through 3mm glass, and recommends the best config.
   7:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner.cpp ****  *
   8:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner.cpp ****  * Usage:
   9:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner.cpp ****  *   1. Flash and open serial monitor
  10:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner.cpp ****  *   2. For each config: keep finger OFF during baseline, then press firmly
  11:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner.cpp ****  *   3. Read recommended registers at the end
  12:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner.cpp ****  */
